---
title: Easy Seared Steak & Chargrilled Capsicum Relish with Veggies & Tomato Salad
description: Colourful, nutritious and flavoursome - these are just a few of the ways we can describe this amazing plate of steak and veggies.
Topped with a punchy chargrilled capsicum relish, your insides will love it just as much as your tastebuds do.

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
